   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "224.280",
   "children": [],
   "end": "227.720",
   "id": "f000067",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Ch\u00fang b\u1eaft c\u1eadu \u0111\u00e0o ti\u1ebfp, nh\u01b0ng r\u00fat c\u1ee5c v\u1eabn ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ea5y g\u00ec h\u1ebft."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "227.720",
   "children": [],
   "end": "232.080",
   "id": "f000068",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Th\u1ebf l\u00e0 ch\u00fang x\u00fam l\u1ea1i t\u1ea9n c\u1eadu, m\u00e3i cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi l\u00f3 d\u1ea1ng."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "232.080",
   "children": [],
   "end": "235.240",
   "id": "f000069",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o c\u1eadu r\u00e1ch b\u01b0\u01a1m v\u00e0 c\u1eadu c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh g\u1ea7n k\u1ec1 c\u00e1i ch\u1ebft."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "235.240",
   "children": [],
   "end": "235.240",
   "id": "f000070",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "235.240",
   "children": [],
   "end": "238.720",
   "id": "f000071",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "\u0110\u1eb1ng n\u00e0o m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ch\u1ebft th\u00ec ti\u1ec1n c\u00f2n qu\u00ed b\u00e1u g\u00ec n\u1eefa."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "238.720",
   "children": [],
   "end": "244.200",
   "id": "f000072",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "C\u1eadu ngh\u0129 v\u00e0 nh\u1edb l\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 luy\u1ec7n kim \u0111an \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng n\u00f3i \u00cdt khi ti\u1ec1n c\u1ee9u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta kh\u1ecfi ch\u1ebft."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "244.200",
   "children": [],
   "end": "253.880",
   "id": "f000073",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Th\u1ebf l\u00e0 c\u1eadu th\u00fa th\u1ef1c T\u00f4i t\u00ecm kho b\u00e1u, r\u1ed3i v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f4i m\u00f4i d\u1eadp n\u00e1t v\u00e0 s\u01b0ng v\u00f9 c\u1eadu k\u1ec3 cho b\u1ecdn kia r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 hai l\u1ea7n m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t kho t\u00e0ng gi\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n Kim T\u1ef1 Th\u00e1p n\u00e0y."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "253.880",
   "children": [],
   "end": "258.320",
   "id": "f000074",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "G\u00e3 c\u00f3 v\u1ebb l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ecf l\u0169 n\u00e0y im l\u1eb7ng m\u1ed9t l\u00fac r\u1ed3i b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ecdn Th\u1ea3 n\u00f3 ra."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "258.320",
   "children": [],
   "end": "259.280",
   "id": "f000075",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "N\u00f3 h\u1ebft s\u1ea1ch r\u1ed3i."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "259.280",
   "children": [],
   "end": "261.720",
   "id": "f000076",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Ch\u1ed7 v\u00e0ng n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc l\u00e0 n\u00f3 l\u1ea5y c\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "261.720",
   "children": [],
   "end": "262.160",
   "id": "f000077",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "262.160",
   "children": [],
   "end": "265.280",
   "id": "f000078",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "C\u1eadu \u00fap m\u1eb7t xu\u1ed1ng c\u00e1t Th\u00f4i b\u1ecdn m\u00ecnh \u0111i, tay \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ecf n\u00f3i."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "265.280",
   "children": [],
   "end": "265.280",
   "id": "f000079",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "265.280",
   "children": [],
   "end": "268.080",
   "id": "f000080",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "R\u1ed3i g\u00e3 quay sang c\u1eadu M\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e2u."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "268.080",
   "children": [],
   "end": "271.600",
   "id": "f000081",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "M\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1eebng n\u00ean ngu xu\u1ea9n th\u1ebf."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "271.600",
   "children": [],
   "end": "277.000",
   "id": "f000082",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ngay ch\u00ednh ch\u1ed7 n\u00e0y, tao c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n m\u01a1 r\u1eb1ng tao ph\u1ea3i \u0111i T\u00e2y Ban Nha, t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 th\u1edd l\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1ee5p l\u1edf m\u00e0 l\u0169 ch\u0103n c\u1eebu th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0a c\u1eebu v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0m ch\u1ed7 tr\u00fa ch\u00e2n."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "277.000",
   "children": [],
   "end": "277.560",
   "id": "f000083",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u00e1o l\u1ec5 c\u00f3 m\u1ecdc m\u1ed9t c\u00e2y c\u1ea7u, d\u01b0\u1edbi r\u1ec5 n\u00f3 ch\u00f4n gi\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t kho v\u00e0ng."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "277.560",
   "children": [],
   "end": "278.520",
   "id": "f000084",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Tao \u0111\u00e2u c\u00f3 ngu \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 m\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t sa m\u1ea1c."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "278.520",
   "children": [],
   "end": "279.160",
   "id": "f000085",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "R\u1ed3i ch\u00fang b\u1ecf \u0111i."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "279.160",
   "children": [],
   "end": "280.200",
   "id": "f000086",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "C\u1eadu l\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady, nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Kim T\u1ef1 Th\u00e1p."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "280.200",
   "children": [],
   "end": "280.960",
   "id": "f000087",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Th\u00e1p m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi c\u1eadu, c\u1eadu c\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea1i."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "280.960",
   "children": [],
   "end": "281.560",
   "id": "f000088",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Tim c\u1eadu tr\u00e0n ng\u1eadp ni\u1ec1m vui."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "281.560",
   "children": [],
   "end": "282.520",
   "id": "f000089",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Gi\u1edd th\u00ec c\u1eadu t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y kho b\u00e1u r\u1ed3i."
   ]
  }
 ]
